---
title: Beef Rump & Dijon-Onion Sauce with Potato Fries & Cheesy Garlic Green Bean Salad
description: Elevate your steak night with a juicy beef rump and caramelised onions flavoured with punchy mustard! Juicy, tender beef pairs perfectly with sweet and tangy caramelised onions, golden potato fries, and a crisp garlicky green bean salad. It’s a hearty, flavour-packed feast that hits all the right notes.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/676cf95bd8e11bf886851646-3f99c616.jpeg
